{"tid":2149033,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★政府今日開始為孕婦提供一次免費自願病毒檢測服務 不過計劃反應冷清","createTime":"2020-08-10T07:59:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T11:54:49.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"afea1c1a119b3ed64ee2742a8f2592f6ddae4324","tid":2149033,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T07:59:22.000Z","msg":"【13:10】政府今日開始，由民政事務總署聯同仁濟醫院，為全港孕婦提供一次免費自願病毒檢測服務，名額5,000個，為期一星期。<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">不過計劃反應冷清</span>，部份自取檢測工具地點都未見大排長龍，有準媽媽前來領取檢測工具時，表明希望「求個安心」，因為倘若醫院要求出示陰性證明時，也可以提早準備。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/508818/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0-%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E5%A2%9E60%E5%A4%9A%E5%AE%97%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E5%80%8B%E6%A1%88-%E5%86%8D%E5%A4%9A%E5%85%A9%E5%90%8D%E5%B9%B4%E9%95%B7%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E4%B8%8D%E6%B2%BB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F508818%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%259C%2580%25E6%2596%25B0-%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF-%25E5%25A2%259E60%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%25AE%2597%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E5%2586%258D%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%2582%25A3%25E8%2580%2585%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25B2%25BB&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mKGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=4783d5a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/508818/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0-%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E5%A2%9E60%E5%A4%9A%E5%AE%97%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E5%80%8B%E6%A1%88-%E5%86%8D%E5%A4%9A%E5%85%A9%E5%90%8D%E5%B9%B4%E9%95%B7%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E4%B8%8D%E6%B2%BB</a>"},{"pid":"5c90211f6c776e9ba31759f5d0a87f2745592eda","tid":2149033,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T07:59:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fac